title: Ep 1861 - Jethalal Ki Zidd
shortDesc: In this episode, Jethalal is firmly obstinate that today he’ll have tea in breakfast by becoming guest at other’s home. So they visit Sodi’s and Babita’s home but everywhere, because of certain reasons he was deprived of tea.

title: Ep 1862 - Jethalal in Jail
shortDesc: Jethalal’s extreme urge to have a cup of tea went into vain. He went to each house of Gokuldham society with a hope of having strong and a refreshing cup of tea but he faced disappointment each time.

title: Ep 1863 - Jethalals Pledge
shortDesc: In this episode, everybody in the police station takes an oath with inspector Chalu Pandey that they will take care of cleanliness of the city.

title: Ep 1864 - Jethalals Mockery
shortDesc: In this episode, Jethalal has become a subject of mockery for everyone after the Tea Incident. All of his friends are sarcastically taunting on him.

title: Ep 1865 - Champaklals Radio
shortDesc: In this episode, after a long time Champaklal has taken out his old classical radio ‘Gaanelal’. Jethalal and his father Champaklal

title: Ep 1866 - Jethalals New Problem
shortDesc: In this episode, Jethalal gets irritated by Bawri. She comes repeatedly to recharge her mobile for 10rupee. Jehthalal tries to convince her to recharge her mobile with a larger amount. While he was persistently trying to convince her.

title: Ep 1867 - Health Consciousness in Gokuldham
shortDesc: It is a healthy day in Gokuldham. Daya persuades Tapu to have milk. After that Bhide gets interrupted by Jethalal while he was returning home from vegetable market. Bhide’s carrot was taken by Gokuldham society member for some or the other reason.

shortDesc: In this episode, Newspaper Vendor of Gokuldham Society has made a mistake by putting Marathi Newspaper in Sodi’s house and Punjabi paper in Bhide’s. However, this chaos brings two culture on the same dining table. While on the other side.

title: Ep 1869 - Jethalal gets irritated by Bagha and Bawri
shortDesc: Bagha is anxious because he forgets shop locker’s keys at Bawri’s home. As soon as he started to exit shop, Jethalal reached there, and he comes to know about the Bagha’s mistake, immediately Jethalal burst in anger and starts scolding.

title: Ep 1870 - Aachar Papad Ka Payment
shortDesc: Bhide has decided to take back Madhavi’s pending payments of Pickle and Papad from Manoj. The payment is due from since last six months and each time Manoj was making some or the other excuses. However, this time Bhide went straight to Manoj’s hous

title: Ep 1871 - Hila Dene Wala Accident
shortDesc: Bhide met a man while returning back from Manoj’s house after taking the payment. The man was completely drunk and was waiting for auto-rickshaw.

title: Ep 1872 - Bhide Needs an Advice
shortDesc: Bhide, while returning back home after taking his due payment from Manoj has got a brief case full of gold. It was Bhide, who has saved a drunkard’s life and that person has happily given him a brief case full of gold!

title: Ep 1873 - Bhides Mid-Night Urgent Meeting
shortDesc: Bhide has got a brief case full of gold in it, he has very secretly brought it to his house. However, Bhide was little confused after getting the brief case full of gold in it and hence, he decided to consult the Gokuldham society members

title: Ep 1874 - Bhides Confusion
shortDesc: Bhide has got a briefcase full of gold and has got tensed after knowing its estimated value in the market. He is seeking advice from his friends to decide the next course of action.

title: Ep 1875 - Bhides Terrifying Dream
shortDesc: Bhide is seeing a dream that thieves has entered inside Jethalal’s house and have stolen the briefcase full of gold at gunpoint. However, Bhide started shouting in his sleep and on waking up he went straight to Jethalal’s house
